name: Manage Cards
description: As a user I want to navigate to the Manage Cards screen so that I can see all my cards

elements.name: Verify the manage cards screen to view cards returned by the Get Cards service call and back navigation

child_steps.name: Click on Manage Card menut item

steps.name: I see the standard loading pulse for manage cards
I must see the manage cards screen "Manage cards" with a back button
I should see the card image "CREDIT CARD" and "5120-5503-0640-5489"

elements.name: Verify the manage cards error screen

steps.name: I navigate to manage card and the service call fails

child_steps.name: Click on Manage Card menut item

steps.name: I must see the  manage cards error screen with "Something went wrong, please try again." and "Reload cards" icon

arguments.val: Something went wrong, please try again.

elements.name: Verify the navigation to stop card screen for a cheque and credit card

child_steps.name: Click on Manage Card menut item

steps.name: I click on the "LOST/STOLEN" button for a cheque card "5120-5503-0640-5489"
I must see the stop card information Screen One "This action can not be undone (once the card is stopped it cannot be used again)."

arguments.val: This action can not be undone (once the card is stopped it cannot be used again).

elements.name: Verify the navigation to dialler for stopping a debit card

child_steps.name: Click on Manage Card menut item

steps.name: I must see the manage cards screen "Manage cards" with a back button
I click on the "LOST/STOLEN " button for a debit card "5520-5770-1204-2997"

child_steps.name: Click on Manage Card menut item
